headline: Pembina Pipeline Q3 Earnings & Revenues Miss Estimates, Both Down Y/Y
summary: PBA expects 2025 adjusted EBITDA in the range of C$4.25 billion to C$4.35 billion compared with the previous guidance of C$4.23 billion to C$4.43 billion.

headline: Delek US Q3 Earnings & Revenues Beat Estimates, Adjusted EBITDA Up Y/Y
summary: DK expects total crude throughput in the range of 252,000-284,000 bpd and total throughput in the band of 271,000-303,000 bpd for the fourth quarter of 2025.
